---
// Admin /admin/leads · Phase 1 localStorage 版
// Phase 2 (Day 10+): 接真 RDS Postgres + Auth.js magic link + /api/leads GET/PATCH
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Admin · Leads · Shipwright"
  description="Shipwright 内部 Admin · Lead 列表"
  path="/admin/leads"
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-6 py-8">
    <header class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
      <div>
        <p
          class="mb-1 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]"
          style="color:var(--color-signal-600)"
        >
          Admin · Shipwright 内部
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold" style="color:var(--fg-display)">
          Leads · 留资线索
        </h1>
      </div>
      <div class="flex gap-2">
        <button
          type="button"
          id="export-csv"
          class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-1.5 rounded-[var(--radius-md)] border px-3 text-sm transition hover:opacity-80"
          style="border-color:var(--border-strong);color:var(--fg-default)"
        >
          导出 CSV
        </button>
        <button
          type="button"
          id="clear-all"
          class="inline-flex h-9 items-center gap-1.5 rounded-[var(--radius-md)] border px-3 text-sm transition hover:opacity-80"
          style="border-color:var(--color-error-500);color:var(--color-error-500)"
        >
          清空所有
        </button>
      </div>
    </header>

    <!-- 计数 -->
    <div class="mb-6 grid grid-cols-5 gap-3 font-mono text-sm" id="stats">
      {[
        { key: "new", label: "New", color: "var(--color-signal-500)" },
        { key: "contacted", label: "Contacted", color: "var(--color-warning-500)" },
        { key: "qualified", label: "Qualified", color: "var(--color-primary-500)" },
        { key: "converted", label: "Converted", color: "var(--color-success-500)" },
        { key: "lost", label: "Lost", color: "var(--color-error-500)" },
      ].map((s) => (
        <div
          class="rounded-[var(--radius-md)] border p-3 text-center"
          style="background:var(--bg-card);border-color:var(--border-default)"
        >
          <div
            class="tabular-nums text-2xl font-bold"
            style={`color:${s.color}`}
            data-count={s.key}
          >0</div>
          <div class="mt-1 text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">
            {s.label}
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>

    <!-- Filter bar -->
    <div class="mb-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-2 text-sm">
      <input
        type="search"
        placeholder="搜姓名/公司/备注..."
        id="filter-search"
        class="h-9 flex-1 min-w-[200px] rounded-[var(--radius-sm)] border px-3"
        style="background:var(--bg-card);border-color:var(--border-strong);color:var(--fg-display)"
      />
      <select
        id="filter-status"
        class="h-9 rounded-[var(--radius-sm)] border px-3"
        style="background:var(--bg-card);border-color:var(--border-strong);color:var(--fg-display)"
      >
        <option value="">全部状态</option>
        <option value="new">New</option>
        <option value="contacted">Contacted</option>
        <option value="qualified">Qualified</option>
        <option value="converted">Converted</option>
        <option value="lost">Lost</option>
      </select>
      <select
        id="filter-gmv"
        class="h-9 rounded-[var(--radius-sm)] border px-3"
        style="background:var(--bg-card);border-color:var(--border-strong);color:var(--fg-display)"
      >
        <option value="">全部 GMV</option>
        <option value="lt_500k">&lt; 500 万</option>
        <option value="500k_2m">500 万-2000 万</option>
        <option value="2m_10m">2000 万-1 亿</option>
        <option value="gt_10m">1 亿+</option>
      </select>
      <select
        id="filter-scene"
        class="h-9 rounded-[var(--radius-sm)] border px-3"
        style="background:var(--bg-card);border-color:var(--border-strong);color:var(--fg-display)"
      >
        <option value="">全部场景</option>
        <option value="v-cs">V-CS 客服</option>
        <option value="v-seo">V-SEO SEO</option>
        <option value="v-ad">V-AD 广告</option>
        <option value="v-content">V-CONTENT 内容</option>
        <option value="v-ops">V-OPS 运营</option>
        <option value="other">其他</option>
      </select>
    </div>

    <!-- Table -->
    <div
      class="overflow-x-auto rounded-[var(--radius-lg)] border"
      style="background:var(--bg-card);border-color:var(--border-default);box-shadow:var(--shadow-sm)"
    >
      <table class="min-w-full text-sm">
        <thead>
          <tr
            class="border-b text-left"
            style="border-color:var(--border-default);background:var(--bg-muted)"
          >
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">姓名</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">联系方式</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">公司</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">GMV</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">场景</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">来源</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">时间</th>
            <th class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.08em]" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">状态</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody id="leads-tbody">
          <tr><td colspan="8" class="px-4 py-12 text-center" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">加载中...</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>

    <div
      class="mt-6 rounded-[var(--radius-md)] border-l-2 p-4 text-sm"
      style="background:var(--bg-muted);border-color:var(--color-signal-500);color:var(--fg-default)"
    >
      <strong style="color:var(--fg-display)">Phase 1 Mock Admin:</strong>
      Lead 数据从 <code style="font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--color-signal-600)">localStorage["shipwright-leads"]</code> 读取 ·
      和首页/Contact 页的 LeadForm 共享同一 key · 真后端 Day 10+ 切换 <code style="font-family:var(--font-mono);color:var(--color-signal-600)">GET /api/leads</code> (RDS + Auth.js).
      <br/><br/>
      <strong>使用方法:</strong> 访问 /contact 填一个测试 lead → 刷新本页就能看到数据 + 可改状态 + 导 CSV.
    </div>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
  (() => {
    const KEY = "shipwright-leads";
    const tbody = document.getElementById("leads-tbody");
    const search = document.getElementById("filter-search");
    const fStatus = document.getElementById("filter-status");
    const fGmv = document.getElementById("filter-gmv");
    const fScene = document.getElementById("filter-scene");

    const gmvLabels = { lt_500k: "<500万", "500k_2m": "500万-2000万", "2m_10m": "2000万-1亿", gt_10m: "1亿+" };
    const sceneLabels = { "v-cs": "V-CS", "v-seo": "V-SEO", "v-ad": "V-AD", "v-content": "V-CONTENT", "v-ops": "V-OPS", other: "其他" };
    const sourceLabels = { baidu: "百度", xiaohongshu: "小红书", wechat: "微信", referral: "推荐", linkedin: "LinkedIn", github: "GitHub", other: "其他" };
    const statusColors = {
      new: { bg: "#FDF3EC", fg: "#A44317" },
      contacted: { bg: "#FFF6E0", fg: "#8A6008" },
      qualified: { bg: "#E8F1FA", fg: "#1E4C80" },
      converted: { bg: "#E8F5EE", fg: "#1E6B40" },
      lost: { bg: "#FCE8E8", fg: "#8C2020" },
    };

    const loadLeads = () => {
      const raw = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(KEY) || "[]");
      return raw.map((l) => ({ ...l, status: l.status || "new" }));
    };
    const saveLeads = (list) => localStorage.setItem(KEY, JSON.stringify(list));

    const matchFilter = (l) => {
      const q = search.value.trim().toLowerCase();
      if (q && !`${l.name} ${l.company || ""} ${l.notes || ""}`.toLowerCase().includes(q)) return false;
      if (fStatus.value && l.status !== fStatus.value) return false;
      if (fGmv.value && l.gmv_band !== fGmv.value) return false;
      if (fScene.value && l.scenario !== fScene.value) return false;
      return true;
    };

    const render = () => {
      const leads = loadLeads();
      // Counts
      const counts = { new: 0, contacted: 0, qualified: 0, converted: 0, lost: 0 };
      leads.forEach((l) => { counts[l.status] = (counts[l.status] || 0) + 1; });
      Object.entries(counts).forEach(([k, v]) => {
        const el = document.querySelector(`[data-count="${k}"]`);
        if (el) el.textContent = v;
      });

      const filtered = leads.filter(matchFilter);
      if (filtered.length === 0) {
        tbody.innerHTML = `<tr><td colspan="8" class="px-4 py-12 text-center" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">
          ${leads.length === 0 ? "localStorage 无数据 · 去 /contact 填一个测试 lead →" : "筛选无结果"}
        </td></tr>`;
        return;
      }
      tbody.innerHTML = filtered.sort((a, b) =>
        new Date(b.createdAt || 0).getTime() - new Date(a.createdAt || 0).getTime()
      ).map((l) => {
        const sc = statusColors[l.status];
        const time = l.createdAt ? new Date(l.createdAt).toLocaleString("zh-CN", { hour12: false }) : "-";
        return `
          <tr class="border-b" style="border-color:var(--border-default)">
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-medium" style="color:var(--fg-display)">${escape(l.name)}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3" style="color:var(--fg-default)">
              <span class="font-mono text-xs" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">${l.contact_type || ""}</span>
              <span class="ml-1">${escape(l.contact_value || "")}</span>
            </td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3" style="color:var(--fg-default)">${escape(l.company || "-")}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">${gmvLabels[l.gmv_band] || "-"}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">${sceneLabels[l.scenario] || "-"}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">${sourceLabels[l.utm_source] || "-"}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3 font-mono text-xs" style="color:var(--fg-muted)">${time}</td>
            <td class="px-4 py-3">
              <select
                data-lead-status="${l.id}"
                class="h-7 rounded-[var(--radius-sm)] px-2 text-xs font-semibold"
                style="background:${sc.bg};color:${sc.fg};border:1px solid ${sc.fg}33"
              >
                ${["new", "contacted", "qualified", "converted", "lost"].map((s) =>
                  `<option value="${s}" ${l.status === s ? "selected" : ""}>${s}</option>`
                ).join("")}
              </select>
            </td>
          </tr>
        `;
      }).join("");

      // Bind status change
      tbody.querySelectorAll("[data-lead-status]").forEach((el) => {
        el.addEventListener("change", (e) => {
          const id = el.dataset.leadStatus;
          const list = loadLeads();
          const lead = list.find((l) => l.id === id);
          if (lead) {
            lead.status = e.target.value;
            lead.updatedAt = new Date().toISOString();
            saveLeads(list);
            render();
          }
        });
      });
    };

    const escape = (s) => String(s || "").replace(/[&<>"']/g, (c) => ({ "&": "&amp;", "<": "&lt;", ">": "&gt;", '"': "&quot;", "'": "&#39;" }[c]));

    [search, fStatus, fGmv, fScene].forEach((el) => el?.addEventListener("input", render));

    document.getElementById("export-csv")?.addEventListener("click", () => {
      const leads = loadLeads();
      if (leads.length === 0) return alert("无数据可导出");
      const headers = ["id", "createdAt", "name", "contact_type", "contact_value", "company", "gmv_band", "scenario", "utm_source", "notes", "status", "sourcePage"];
      const csv = [headers.join(",")].concat(
        leads.map((l) => headers.map((h) => `"${String(l[h] || "").replace(/"/g, '""')}"`).join(","))
      ).join("\n");
      const blob = new Blob(["﻿" + csv], { type: "text/csv;charset=utf-8" });
      const url = URL.createObjectURL(blob);
      const a = document.createElement("a");
      a.href = url;
      a.download = `shipwright-leads-${new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 10)}.csv`;
      a.click();
      URL.revokeObjectURL(url);
    });

    document.getElementById("clear-all")?.addEventListener("click", () => {
      if (!confirm("确定清空所有 leads? 此操作不可恢复 (Phase 1 localStorage only).")) return;
      localStorage.removeItem(KEY);
      render();
    });

    render();
  })();
  </script>
</BaseLayout>
